Chavez Approves $2 Billion for China Joint Development Fund

-- B y   C o r i n a   R o d r i g u e z   P o n s   a n d   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 
2011-07-09T22:49:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-09/chavez-approves-2-billion-for-china-joint-development-fund.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez ,
speaking on state television, approved  Venezuela ’s $2 billion
contribution to a joint development fund with  China .  Venezuela’s contribution comes from the Fonden and China
will contribute another $4 billion, Chavez said. Venezuela will
pay China over two years with oil shipments, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Corina Pons in Caracas at 
